		<title>New Zine about Self-Care: Self as Other</title>
		<link>http://www.crimethinc.com/blog/2013/09/06/new-zine-about-self-care-self-as-other/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2013 18:46:20 +0000</pubDate>
